<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 25. Neighbour-joining tree based on p-distance of all COI sequences (> 550 bp) for which specimens were examined. Each terminal includes the species name, BOLD process ID number, country of collection, and Barcode Index Number. Red text indicates the presence of more than one named species grouped under a single BIN (BIN merge)." , "Figure 8. Female heads A D. spinitarsis B D. pribilofensis C D. setibasis. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." , "Figure 5. Tarsomeres A D. pribilofensis, male fore tarsomeres 3 - 5 B D. spinitarsis, male mid tarsomere 1 C D. spinitarsis, female mid tarsomere 1 D D. quadrisetosa, male fore tarsomeres 1 - 5. Scale bars: 0.25 mm." , "Figure 4. Male head, lateral view A D. pribilofensis B D. neoborealis C D. vockerothi D D. spinitarsis E D. glacialis F D. santamonicae G D. amnicola H D. minor. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520366" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520349" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520346" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520345" .

